The proposed method involves learning dictionaries and sparse representation, which are techniques commonly used in machine learning (cs.LG) and signal processing (cs.MM). The paper also mentions the use of progressive schemes and optimization algorithms, which are topics related to information theory (cs.IT) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
